<td width="490"top"><a href="/auction.html" class="linkbold">WentworthAuction</a><br /><img src="/i/s.gif" width="1" height="3"><br />

An auction platform in which states, state agencies and other institutional investors can receive bids for the reinvestment of proceeds from bond issues.  In addition, providers of investment contracts and repurchase agreements can bid for the investment of state, agency and municipal funds.</td>

